snippet: Borussia Dortmund missed a bagful of chances to draw 1-1 at home with Augsburg on Tuesday, as they squandered the opportunity to make up ground in the Bundesliga title race heading into the winter break....
lead_paragraph: Borussia Dortmund missed a bagful of chances to draw 1-1 at home with Augsburg on Tuesday, as they squandered the opportunity to make up ground in the Bundesliga title race heading into the winter break.

headline.main: Dortmund Stumble Against Augsburg, Eintracht Win Again
headline.print_headline: Dortmund Stumble Against Augsburg, Eintracht Win Again
